Package com.jensen.model

This package contains "model" relevant classes pursuant to the MVC designing pattern.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    SumoDAO
    This interface implements methods, used to communicate with database mananger (MySQL), on the CRUD terms.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Club
    This class implements a club object representing a sumo club.
    ClubTableModel
    This class implements converting from a LinkedList with Club object to a TableModel representing a table with sumo clubs.
    Coach
    This class implements a coach object representing a sumo caoch.
    CoachTableModel
    This class implements converting from a LinkedList with Coach object to a TableModel representing a table with sumo coaches.
    Model
    This class implements the connection to the sumo database manager (MySQL), using Java Database Connectivity (JDBC).
    Player
    This class implements a player object representing a sumo player.
    PlayerTableModel
    This class implements converting from a LinkedList with Player object to a TableModel representing a table with sumo players.
